Introduction

Jang Jiho is a South Korean singer under FirstOne Entertainment. He debuted in 2022 as the maknae of the boy group NINE.i.

On December 29th, Jiho was revealed to be one of the participants of the survival show "Boys Planet."

On March 2, Jiho was eliminated from "Boys Planet." in episode 5 after ranking 63rd place.
